            <p><span class="strong"><strong>Ghoul Fever (Su):</strong></span> Disease-bite, Fortitude DC 15, incubation period 1 day, damage 1d3 Con and 1d3 Dex. The save DC is Charisma-based.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
